text: Baldwin V of Hainaut (1150 – 17 December 1195) was count of Hainaut (1171–1195), margrave of Namur as Baldwin I (1189–1195) and count of Flanders as Baldwin VIII (1191–1195). Category:1150s births Category:1190s deaths Category:Counts of Namur Category:Counts of Hainaut
title: Baldwin V, Count of Hainaut
